source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_00<tab>Byrglaent, the master vintner of Wineport, is having difficulty acquiring good cork.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_00<tab>Byrglaent scheint sich über etwas aufzuregen.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_01<tab>Byrglaent is nearly apoplectic over the quality of the cork he has been supplied. Not willing to settle for anything less than first-rate, he has bid you slay five cork bulbs.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_01<tab>Byrglaent ärgert sich über die schlechte Qualität der Korken, mit denen die Weinflaschen verschlossen sind. Er bittet dich, fünf <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F202AC030502 /var> zu erlegen, um <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E870E030502 /var> einzusammeln.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_02<tab>You have slain five cork bulbs and ripped the quality cork from their lifeless corpses. Deliver the haul to Byrglaent in Wineport.

TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_03<tab>The master vintner extols the virtues of the high-quality cork you have acquired. However, he cannot help but lament over his own staff's lack of ability when it comes to gathering the material themselves.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_SEQ_03<tab>Die neuen Korken scheinen Byrglaent zu gefallen. Wein scheint für ihn eine wichtige Angelegenheit zu sein.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_TODO_00<tab>Gather impeccable cork from cork bulbs.

TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_000<tab>You call this cork? Pah! This sad, squelchy thing isn't fit to kiss my back end, let alone my fine whites and reds. I'd say you should try again, except that I wouldn't trust you with the <var 1A 02 /var>worst<var 1A 01 /var> of vintages now. You're dead to me!
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_000<tab>Dieser vermaledeite Korken! Da gibt man sich Mühe, den besten Wein in ganz Eorzea herzustellen, und dann wird einem der Genuss von bröseligen Korken vermiest!

source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_001<tab><var 1A 02 /var>You<var 1A 01 /var>! Adventurer! I've had it trying to get quality from my own lot. Show this oaf how it's done and bring me the materials you find off cork bulbs. Harvesting five of them should do. Time flies and uncorked wine sours! Go, go!
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_001<tab>Würdest du mir fünf <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E870E030502 /var> besorgen? Die kannst du <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 03F202AC030402 /var> abnehmen, wenn du sie tüchtig durchschüttelst.
TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_DUMMY_000_010<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F202AC01 /var>を5体討伐し、「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E870E01 /var>」をゲット

source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_020<tab>Where is that cork I asked for? If you believe that loitering will secure you a glass of something, you are very much mistaken. <var 1A 02 /var>And<var 1A 01 /var> possibly dead to me!
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_020<tab>Und? Hast du mir Material für neue Korken besorgen können? Es muss aber schon hochwertiger Kork sein.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_021<tab>Now <var 1A 02 /var>this<var 1A 01 /var> seems like some fine cork. Hmmm, just the right amount of give...some air comes through, but not the moisture. I should be so lucky as to have barrels full of this. If only <var 1A 02 /var>my<var 1A 01 /var> people were as efficient at finding it...
target: TEXT_GAIUSB211_00842_BYRGLAENT_000_021<tab>Hm, naja, nicht von allerbester Qualität, aber besser als der Schund, den ich eben in meinem Wein schweben hatte. Ein schlechter Korken kann den besten Wein ruinieren. Danke für deine Hilfe.
